reviewText: I loved it, very informative and A well made documentary about the city where Jesus lived and preached the most.  A must buy if you are interested in the things of God!
Not what I was looking for. I wanted to hear about the history of Capernaum. Instead it was a sermon.
As always, love these DVDs. They are so rich in detail.
I love to study the history of the bible & this DVD gave me new knowledge. Sure is interesting that Capernaum had the SAVIOR right will them & many didn't believe!!

This movie was very powerful.  Capernaum is where Jesus spent most of his ministry and where he performed most of his miracles.  Good narration - biblical references - all around good lesson.  Would recommend to anyone wanting to learn about our Lord.
